internal.content: --- title: "General Troubleshooting" date: 2022-11-03T10:57:46+01:00 weight: 301 --- ![ibm](./../images/ibm/automation-welcome-tour.gif) ## Official Troubleshooting Documentation The official IBM Troubleshooting Documentation is probably a safe place to start. ## Check your installation Run the following tool: ```bash ./tools/11_check_install.sh ``` This might give you some pointers as to why your instance is misbehaving.
